column2: SELECT Top # s.ra, s.dec, s.z from GalSpecLine AS q JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = q.specobjid JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN Galaxy AS g ON s.bestobjid = G.objid WHERE (G.Flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = # and s.class = &&& and s.zwarning = # and p.petroRad_r < # and (p.u - p.r) < # - #*(p.g) and s.class = &&& and s.z <=#
